<item>
            <title>[SPARK-25134] Csv column pruning with checking of headers throws incorrect error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-25134</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;hello!&lt;br/&gt;
seems to me there is some interaction between csv column pruning and the checking of csv headers that is causing issues. for example this fails:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-scala&quot;&gt;
Seq((&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;columnA&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;columnB&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).write
  .format(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;csv&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
  .option(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;header&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)
  .save(dir)
spark.read
  .format(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;csv&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
  .option(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;header&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)
  .option(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;enforceSchema&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;)
  .load(dir)
  .select(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;columnA&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
  .show
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the error is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
291.0 (TID 319, localhost, executor driver): java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Number of column &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; CSV header is not equal to number of fields &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; the schema:
[info]  Header length: 1, schema size: 2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if i remove the project it works fine. if i disable column pruning it also works fine.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
